text: Magdalena Partido () is a partido in the northeastern part of Buenos Aires Province in Argentina. The provincial subdivision has a population of about 16,000 inhabitants in an area of , and its capital city is Magdalena, which is from Buenos Aires. ==Settlements== *Magdalena *General Mansilla (Estación Bartolomé Bavio) *Atalaya *Vieytes Category:Partidos of Buenos Aires Province Category:States and territories established in 1611
